name: TWILIGHT Fine Art Portrait
description:
Pencil portrait of the main characters from "Twilight." Depicted are the characters Edward Cullen and Bella Swan (as portrayed by Robert Pattinson and Kristen Stewart).

Fine art prints are on 8.5" x 11" heavy card stock and individually hand-signed by me, the artist.



If you have any questions, or are interested in commissioning an original piece, please contact me at xtinajohnson@gmail.com
